VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT Response\.Write\(.*\)
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(Request\.|HttpContext\.Current\.Request) && MISSING:(HtmlEncode|HttpUtility\.HtmlEncode|AntiXssEncoder|TagBuilder)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of Response.Write without output encoding, which can lead to cross-site scripting vulnerabilities.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Untrusted Input Handling in HTLM Output: Response.Write.
